20traffic%20control%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20now%2C%20its%20main%20runway%20is%20closed%20for%20construction%20until%20at%20least%20June%2C%20and%20classic%20April%20rain%20showers%20have%20only%20made%20things%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAtmosphere%20Research%20Group%20travel%20analyst%20Henry%20%3Cspan%3EHarteveldt%3C%2Fspan%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20those%20stuck%20in%20chaos%20should%20keep%20their%20wits%2C%20and%20those%20traveling%20in%20the%20near%20future%20may%20want%20to%20consider%20the%20New%20York%20City%20area's%20other%20airports%20or%20another%20United%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223699b145-39a6-4b02-8504-0531f466463f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAvoid%20Newark%20or%20brace%20for%20inevitable%20disruptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York's%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20International%20Airport%20and%20LaGuardia%20Airport%20are%20the%20most%20obvious%20alternatives%20to%20Newark%2C%20but%20%3Cspan%3EHarteveldt%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20there's%20also%20Long%20Island%20MacArthur%20Airport%20and%20Westchester%20Airport%20in%20White%20Plains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20suburban%20options%20are%20further%20from%20the%20city%2C%20and%20they%20won't%20have%20the%20same%20plethora%20of%20flight%20connections.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-adds-new-laguardia-airport-routes-perimeter-rule-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELaGuardia%2C%20which%20has%20a%20perimeter%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20only%20allows%20flights%20longer%20than%201%2C500%20miles%2C%20like%20United's%20flight%20to%20Denver%2C%20on%20Saturdays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENerdWallet%20travel%20analyst%20Sally%20French%20told%20BI%20to%20allow%20plenty%20of%20extra%20time%20for%20your%20connection%20if%20Newark%20is%20your%20only%20option.%20She%20added%20that%20customers%20should%20avoid%20checking%20a%20bag%20as%20carry-on%20only%20allows%20for%20more%20flexibility%20to%20switch%20flights%20or%20airport