t%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20customers%20should%20ask%20to%20be%20booked%20on%20one%20of%20United's%20partner%20airlines%20if%20their%20original%20flight%20is%20disrupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Newark%20is%20your%20only%20option%2C%20gird%20your%20loins%20and%20pack%20your%20patience%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Cspan%3EHarteveldt%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20customers%20should%20not%20vent%20their%20frustrations%20at%20the%20airline's%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de2009a7-1af7-49b4-994a-42973070bc2f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20things%20got%20so%20bad%20at%20Newark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20major%20airports%20to%20experience%20days%20of%20disruptions%20due%20to%20weather%20and%20equipment%2C%20like%20the%20January%20winter%20storms%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-crowdstrike-outage-cost-170-million-customer-crew-expenses-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrowdStrike%20fiasco%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20a%20combination%20of%20factors%20coexist%2C%20things%20can%20get%20extra%20chaotic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202024%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20moved%20the%20ATC%20arrivals%20operation%20that%20handles%20Newark%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Philadelphia%20to%20address%20staffing%20issues%2C%20though%20the%20same%20problem%20has%20appeared%20regardless%20of%20where%20the%20traffic%20flows.%20Equipment%20failures%20at%20the%20facility%20have%20only%20added%20to%20the%20backups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20closure%20of%20the%20airport's%20busiest%20runway%20is%20expected%20to%20last%20until%20at%20least%20June%20as%20planes%20wait%20to%20use%20alternates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20monitor%20shows%20flight%20delays%20at%20Newark%20International%20Airport%20on%20May%205.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681926cf3fe8d3928364fbdd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20h