ilitary%20Police%20officers%20stand%20on%20an%20elevated%20platform%20as%20fans%20wait%20for%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20free%20mega-concert%20of%20US%20pop%20star%20Lady%20Gaga%20at%20Copacabana%20beach%20in%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro%2C%20Brazil%2C%20on%20May%203%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6819188cc6ad288d14800da7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222033%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVictor%20Nascimento%20and%20his%20friends%20avoided%20drinking%20too%20much%20as%20to%20avoid%20having%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%20in%20the%20crowded%20beach.%3Cp%3EDaniel%20RAMALHO%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20know%20that%20my%20experience%20of%20getting%20in%20wasn't%20the%20same%20as%20everyone's.%20Packed%20transport%2C%20security%20checks%2C%20and%20long%20lines%20made%20it%20really%20difficult%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20to%20get%20onto%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9d575ba-0ad1-46ca-a007-cee93ec2a18d%5C%22%3EThe%20show%20was%20incredible%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20she%20started%20performing%2C%20we%20watched%2C%20jumped%2C%20and%20screamed%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%20It%20was%20incredible.%20People%20were%20dressed%20like%20Lady%20Gaga%2C%20crying%20through%20the%20concert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20surrounding%20me%20was%20either%20LGBTQ%2B%20or%20a%20supporter%20of%20the%20community.%20It%20was%20such%20a%20special%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20to%20see%202%20million%20people%20waving%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20flag%2C%20especially%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20fighting%20the%20crowds%20to%20leave%2C%20we%20stayed%20and%20watched%20the%20after-show%2C%20a%20DJ%2C%20until%20the%20beach%20had%20cleared%20out.%20When%20we%20left%20to%20get%20food%2C%20the%20beach%20was%20much%20quieter.%20I%20finally%20got%20back%20to%20the%20hotel%20at%203%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229831b196-aaea-4b4c-87d4-fd08765d395b%5C%22%3EI%20spent%20a