n%20in%20resource%20management%20decisions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20women%20roll%20thousands%20of%20%3Cem%3Ebeedis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(leaf-rolled%20cigarettes)%20at%20home%2C%20earning%20low%20wages%2C%20working%20in%20hazardous%20conditions%2C%20and%20often%20lacking%20access%20to%20basic%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20regions%20and%20sectors%2C%20women%20workers%20share%20a%20common%20reality%3A%20being%20part%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20vast%20informal%20economy.%20However%2C%20their%20roles%20come%20with%20gendered%20challenges%2C%20compounded%20by%20unsafe%20working%20conditions%2C%20lack%20of%20job%20security%2C%20exploitative%20wages%2C%20and%20systemic%20neglect.%20Women%20in%20these%20sectors%20are%20often%20disproportionately%20affected%2C%20enduring%20not%20just%20economic%20hardship%20but%20a%20lack%20of%20safety%20and%20dignity%20in%20their%20workplaces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20employment%20in%202017-2018%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20461.52%20million%20(according%20to%20the%202017-18%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey).%20The%20informal%20economy%20encompasses%20jobs%2C%20enterprises%2C%20and%20workers%20that%20exist%20outside%20state%20regulation%20or%20protection.%20These%20roles%20rarely%20offer%20fixed%20wages%2C%20job%20security%2C%20or%20benefits.%20Workers%20here%20navigate%20a%20world%20without%20contracts%2C%20safety%20nets%2C%20or%20social%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20informal%20work%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20always%20equate%20to%20poverty%2C%20it%20often%20comes%20perilously%20close.%20And%20once%20a%20family%20slips%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%2C%20climbing%20back%20is%20an%20uphill%20battle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrassroots%20organisations%20are%20stepping%20in%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap%2C%20offering%20informal%20workers%20much-needed%20protection%2C%20voice%2C%20and%20measures%20to%20enable%20greater%20economic%20resilience%2C%20collective%20agency%2C%20and%20access%20to%20opportunities%20that%20can%20help%20them%20build%20more%20secure%20futures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20article%20explores%20how%20three%20select%20grassroots%20organisations%20are%20addressing%20the%20unique%20challenges%20faced%20by%20informal%20workers%20across%20India%20and%20how%20they%20are%20driving%20transformative%20change%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJute%20mill%20and%20tea%20garden%20workers%20of%20West%20Bengal%3A%20securing%20safe%20and%20equitable%20workplaces%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20tea%20gardens%20and%20jute%20mills%2C%20sexual%20harassment%20remains%20a%20deeply%20underreported%20and%20poorly%20understood%20issue.%20With%20the%20jute%20mills%20employing%20approximately%2025%2C000%20women%20(a%20number%20on%20the%20rise)%20and%20tea%20plantations%20historically%20providing%20livelihood%20for%20about%202%2C00%2C000%20women%20workers%2C%20these%20sectors%20are%20critical%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20both%20industries%20lack%20comprehensive%20information%20on%20the%20safety%20of%20women%20workers%2C%20especially%20concerning%20sexual%20harassment.%20For%20many%20women%2C%20these%20acts%20are%20not%20even%20identified%20as%20violations.%20They%20have%20become%20part%20of%20the%20everyday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20critical%20gap%20and%20advocate%20for%20safer%20workplaces%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsanhita-grc.org%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSanhita%2527s%2520beginning%2520was%2520located%2520in%2CConference%2520on%2520Women%252C%2520Beijing%25201995.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanhita%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Kolkata-based%20gender%20resource%20centre%2C%20undertook%20situation%20analysis%20studies%20in%20both%20the%20jute%20and%20tea%20sectors%20during%202019%20and%202022%2C%20respectively.%20These%20studies%20aimed%20to%20delve%20into%20the%20safety%20of%20women%20workers%2C%20specifically%20focusing%20on%20sexual%20harassment%20at%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20examined%20the%20prevalence%20and%20perceptions%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20the%20accountability%20of%20key%20stakeholders%20in%20ensuring%20safe%20workplaces%2C%20and%20the%20implementation%20status%20of%20the%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(Prevention%2C%20Prohibition%20and%20Redressal)%20Act%2C%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20findings%20from%20both%20studies%20reveal%20a%20startling%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20all%20major%20respondents%20regarding%20safe%20workplaces%2C%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20and%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%202013%20Act.%20Compliance%20with%20the%20Act%20was%20found%20to%20be%20minimal%2C%20and%20the%20issue%20of%20safe%20workplaces%20in%20the%20context%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20was%20not%20considered%20a%20fundamental%20aspect%20of%20working%20conditions%20or%20a%20labour%20issue%20for%20women%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-500x262.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Orientation%20on%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20at%20the%20workplace%20for%20tea%20garden%20workers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-150x79.jpg